      "comment": "FREESPOOL (5) boasts a strong record this course with three wins and two minors from eight tries. Was out of placings last time (17.72) at Mandurah in a Grade 6, finishing seventh and beaten 6 lengths. Rates a leading player. SHADOW MAC (1) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing sixth (16.71) in a Grade 6 at Cannington. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Can measure up this time. WIZARD'S NOVA (2) turned in a plain performance last time when seventh at this track over 297m behind Go Gettem Beryl (18.23) in a Grade 6. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings five times from nine starts. One of the better chances. CHAROS JOURNEY (7) is another with top-three prospects.",
